%% Diagram: Transport Decision Tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Need real-time sync] --> B{Bidirectional?}
    B -->|"server -> client only"| D{HTTP/2 or HTTP/3 available?}
    D -->|Yes| E[SSE]
    D -->|"No / restricted proxy"| F[SSE with HTTP/1.1 fallback]
    E --> EU{Client also uplinks?}
    F --> EU
    EU -->|Yes, infrequent| G[SSE plus HTTP POST]
    EU -->|No| H[SSE only]

    B -->|"both directions"| I{Greenfield, Chromium-leading OK?}
    I -->|Yes| J[WebTransport over HTTP/3]
    I -->|"No, need cross-browser parity"| K[WebSocket]

    J --> L{Offline support needed?}
    K --> L
    L -->|Yes| M[Add IndexedDB queue plus reconnect with replay]
    L -->|No| N[Connection manager plus heartbeats]

    O{Restricted enterprise proxy blocks WS and SSE?} -.fallback.-> P[Long polling]
    K -.fallback when blocked.-> O
